            "title": "騰訊(00700)斥約5億元回購98.2萬股",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　《經濟通通訊社28日專訊》騰訊控股(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00700:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00700\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00700-HK</a>)申報,今日斥約5億元回購98.2萬股,每股最高價515.5元,每股最低價503.5元。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　　該集團根據購回授權所購回股份數目累計約2.72億股,佔2.89103%股權。</p></section><section><p class=\"\">(kl)</p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\"></p></section></main>",
